public interface ISeriesProcessorFactory<A extends Comparable<A>,O extends Comparable<O>>

Factory for ISeriesProcessor. The values from getInputSeriesNames() should be used as tags of the input series when wiring the processor. The values from getConfigurationKeys() must be used to provide the configuration to the factory method. Configuration can be validated prior to be used.
